        "subject": "LU-2139 debug: Add debug info on test unmount",
        "message": "LU-2139 debug: Add debug info on test unmount\n\nThis change is for debugging a Maloo failure only. It is not meant to\nland on any official branch. To get a better handle on why 4245 is\nfailing, I want to know if the OSTs are all up and see the unstable\nstats for clients when they are unmounted.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: Idff961115effd11102a2a2758d28af3e36bd9a93\n"
